llm_output:
SELECT 
    T1.Id, 
    T1.Maker
FROM 
    car_makers AS T1
JOIN (
    SELECT 
        Maker
    FROM 
        model_list
    GROUP BY 
        Maker
    HAVING 
        COUNT(Model) >= 2
) AS T2 ON T1.Id = T2.Maker
JOIN (
    SELECT 
        T3.Maker
    FROM 
        car_names AS T3
    GROUP BY 
        T3.Maker
    HAVING 
        COUNT(MakeId) > 3
) AS T4 ON T1.Id = T4.Maker
